      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON DOLLY (6) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (27.99) at this track behind Aston Barbie in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Top chance in this line up. IOMMI (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (20.46) in a Grade 5 at Grafton. Has a good record here including two wins. Has ability and is one of the better chances. DRILL BABY (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (28.56) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here including four wins. Hard to knock her form from this box, unbeaten in two starts. Has ability and can measure up. HE'S A BONUS (2) can feature with the right run.",
